/* C:\Users\Edwin Boston\OneDrive\Desktop\III\STDLIB\iii\numera\rsa.iii
 *
 * III STDLIB - numera::rsa -- RSA-3072 / RSA-4096 signatures (RSASSA-PSS,
 * RFC 8017 / FIPS 186).  RITCHIE Stage 4.11.  EMSA-PSS encode/verify over
 * SHA-256 with MGF1-SHA-256; RSA primitive via rsa_modexp (constant-time
 * u32-limb Montgomery CIOS; s=m^d mod n, m=s^e mod n).  Keygen primality
 * (Miller-Rabin) uses bigint_modpow.  Keys are arena-bigints (n, e, d).
 * Size-generic over modBits.
 *
 * Public surface (key as bigint IDs + modBits; arena owned by caller):
 *   rsa_pss_sign(arena, n, d, modBits, mHash32, salt, sLen, sig_out) -> i32
 *   rsa_pss_verify(arena, n, e, modBits, mHash32, sig, sigLen, sLen) -> u8 (1=ok)
 *   rsa_os2ip / rsa_i2osp -- octet-string <-> bigint bridge (BE).
 *
 * Hexad: kind_prove.  Ring: R3.  K: 1.00.
 */

